docs/impl/wp_sched_review/logs/S2_T1.2_review.1.stdout.log:32:Every call site is `_ = _resolve_review_schedule_path(...)`. Acceptable for T1.2 scope (T3.2 is "thread review-schedule through swim execution"), but at minimum capture the result into a named local (`review_schedule_path`) and either pass it as `--review-schedule` to the Go subprocess or add a `# T3.2: thread this` placeholder. As written, a follow-up developer has to rewire four call sites and re-test.
